A tower, one of the TwoTowers, that looms over the South pole in ["Austra"] opposite the ["BorealTower"].  The tower is the entrance to the ["Dwarf"] caves.  The other of the two tower is the ["BorealTower"] at the north pole.

 * is a ["Building"], ["Haunted"]
 * is from ["Austra"]

